<td width="550" style="padding: 5px; background-color: #dd0000"><strong style="color: #ffffff;">Concert AD'HOC - 28 MARS 2009 - Epinay sur Orge</strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="550" style="padding: 10px;" bgcolor="#cccccc">
<p><a style="color: #000000;" href="http://www.adhocmusic.com/age3538.php"><img src="http://www.adhocmusic.com/img/get.php/172/244/ffffff/agenda/4323" width="172" height="244" border="0" align="right"/></a></p>
<p>Les groupes au programme seront :</p>
<ul>
<li><a style="color: #000000;" href="http://www.adhocmusic.com/thetoads"><strong>THE TOADS</strong></a> (Rock)</li>
